description:
Job Description

The incumbent will be responsible for monitoring the food quality and restaurant operations to make sure it reaches the Group standard of Jollibee.  Besides reviewing customers’ feedbacks to recommend for improvement plans, the incumbent will develop and maintain operation procedures, identify best practices and lead the team to implement continuous improvement projects and drive for timely results with services quality.

Requirements:

                  Bachelor Degree holder;
                  At least 5 years of solid experience in fast food chain operations, including at least 3 years taking managerial positions in restaurant services quality and shop operations;
                  Hands on experience in developing and implementing standard operating procedures, monitoring services quality and operations and processing assessments to measure compliance with standards;
                  Well familiar with traditional Filipino fast food cuisine, with excellent knowledge of Filipino food culture and recipe;
                  Comprehensive knowledge and experience in fast food chain operations;
                  Good knowledge of the best practice, services standard and management style of reputable chain restaurants, preferably Jollibee’s;
                  Strong analytical, leadership and communication skills;
                  Fluent English and preferably Tagalog.
